Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.93,0:01:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.65,0:01:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Set...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.86,0:01:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa... Kona-chan, you're amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.60,0:01:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How come you don't join any sports clubs even though you're so athletic?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.17,0:01:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if I join a club...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.26,0:01:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't get to watch anime during prime time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Tsukasa, from which side do you eat a Choco Cornet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.44,0:02:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... from the head, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.12,0:02:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.10,0:02:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, which side is the head?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.31,0:02:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The fat side or the skinny side?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.01,0:02:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the skinny side is the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.63,0:02:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought the fatter side was the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.32,0:02:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But why's the skinny side the head?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.47,0:02:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's kind of like a shell, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.68,0:02:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you think the fat side is its head, Kona-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.93,0:02:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's kind of like a caterpillar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.55,0:02:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A caterpillar!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.90,0:02:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But now that you mention it, I guess the shell fits its image better.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.81,0:03:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,U-um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.20,0:03:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You could also tear pieces off the skinny side and use them to eat the chocolate that squirts out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.05,0:03:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really smart, Miyuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.87,0:03:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, everyone can eat it how they choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.50,0:03:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you eat a cream puff?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.60,0:03:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? A cream puff?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.72,0:03:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see... First, I'd split it in two.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.33,0:03:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And dip the top half into the cream in the bottom half.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.10,0:03:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,When I'm done with the top, I'd eat the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.35,0:03:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That way, the cream won't squirt out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.62,0:03:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you can eat the crème and the choux proportionally.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.67,0:03:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You know the kind that has custard and whipped cream in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.21,0:03:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you eat those?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.93,0:03:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mix them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.00,0:03:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I actually wouldn't mix those.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.94,0:03:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But how would you mix them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.20,0:03:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I dunno... I just thought I'd ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,When do you eat the strawberries on top of a strawberry shortcake or the chestnut on top of a Mont Blanc cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see... It depends on the amount of strawberries that are in between the two spongy areas of the cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.76,0:04:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Strawberry, whipped cream, sponge cake...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.71,0:04:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I try to think of the proportions of the volumes when I eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.78,0:04:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So, when it comes to eating the strawberry on top, it depends on the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.77,0:04:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... that sounds pretty foolproof.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.38,0:04:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I usually save it until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.91,0:04:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But sometimes, I get full and I can't finish it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.39,0:04:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,or my family members eat it before I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.91,0:04:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You really have to eat the best first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.02,0:04:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I think of it, I've never seen my sister get her strawberry taken from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.04,0:04:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Kagami for you... Totally cautious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.24,0:04:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you eat the last bite of a popsicle without dropping it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.56,0:04:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You drop them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.84,0:04:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you don't eat it properly...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.58,0:04:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.09,0:04:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Kona-chan, how do you eat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.48,0:04:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I lick it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.11,0:04:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.06,0:04:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How about if you spin it like this while eating it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.93,0:04:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.47,0:05:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually don't like soft-cream that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.52,0:05:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.95,0:05:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like how I'm always stuck with the cone when I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.78,0:05:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you'll always get stuck with the cone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.33,0:05:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I push the soft cream down as I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.76,0:05:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you push it in?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.91,0:05:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,While you eat it, you kind of just go *gui gui* and push it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.61,0:05:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,*gui gui* ...is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.75,0:05:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki-chan, you put a big emphasis on balance, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.00,0:05:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, what do you do with curry rice?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.26,0:05:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mix the rice with the curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.41,0:05:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't mix them, but I try to eat them evenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I just mix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.49,0:05:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you, Kona-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.27,0:05:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It all depends on the curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.92,0:05:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If I poured sauce on top or dropped a raw egg on it, I'd probably mix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sauce on curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.21,0:05:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.77,0:05:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you put sauce on sunny-side up eggs?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.88,0:05:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, I put soy sauce on sunny-side up eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.26,0:05:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? I put mayonnaise on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.78,0:05:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Not just on hard-boiled eggs, but on sunny-side up eggs, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.75,0:05:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep... Mayonnaise goes with most egg dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.50,0:06:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you put it on curry, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.33,0:06:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... I put it on white rice and stuff like beef bowls, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.61,0:06:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It goes really well with the sweet sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.55,0:06:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I put it on oyako-don, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.12,0:06:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Chicken and egg are like relatives, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.67,0:06:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So I put mayonnaise on it since it's made from eggs and call it a "family bowl."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.20,0:06:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.18,0:06:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And although I'm not too fond of natto, if I put mayonnaise on it, I can eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.67,0:06:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh... I can't imagine that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.33,0:06:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, but I think mayonnaise goes best on soft-boiled eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.79,0:06:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't fully cook my sunny-side up eggs, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.28,0:06:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad really likes it this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.35,0:06:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he also likes to pop the yoke and let it ooze out like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.73,0:06:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, if you overcook it, it won't ooze properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.71,0:06:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you eat yakitori?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.79,0:06:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you eat it while it's on the skewer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Or do you take it off the skewer first with your chopsticks?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.30,0:06:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.10,0:06:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm eating one by myself, I'll just eat it off the skewer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.24,0:06:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm sharing one with a group, I'll take it off with my chopsticks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.64,0:06:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.88,0:07:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And isn't it awkward when there's one piece left?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.63,0:07:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's really hard to eat that last piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.69,0:07:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Time passes by as no-one touches it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And it starts to get dry and unpleasant, so it seems like no one's going to eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.73,0:07:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But when the waiter comes to take it away, you say, "Wait, I'm still working on that!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.64,0:07:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Then in the end, you leave the store without eating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.38,0:07:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a waste, isn't it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.01,0:07:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I kind of feel sorry for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.16,0:07:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't you also feel sorry for the meat that gets burnt black and stuck on the grill when you grill?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.85,0:07:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're eating grilled meat, you have to cook it while talking to others, so it's a pretty difficult task.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.89,0:07:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Negi-tan shio cooks really quickly, so it really keeps you busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.64,0:07:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... And when you flip it over once, the other side is already cooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.73,0:07:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Flip it over?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.86,0:07:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.52,0:07:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Salted beef tongue with onions?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.65,0:07:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.15,0:07:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't flip negi-tan shio over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.11,0:07:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Because if you flip it over, the onions on the top will fall off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.19,0:07:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.72,0:08:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,For those, you just let the fire go through and cook it naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.41,0:08:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.57,0:08:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do that from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.19,0:08:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So don't ever flip it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.56,0:08:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's how it works...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.71,0:08:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.81,0:08:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.11,0:08:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.80,0:08:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, the fat side or the skinny side... Which is the head of a Choco Cornet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.48,0:08:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.78,0:08:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so radical.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.89,0:08:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't there been a lot of false imprisonment cases lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.70,0:08:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Where girls are made to call someone "Master" and stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.40,0:08:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.41,0:08:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But rather than being an issue with morals and stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.51,0:08:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,it seems like the guys just played too many ero-games or bishoujo games.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a common situation in those games, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.03,0:08:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak for yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. How do you know the contents of adult games,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.46,0:08:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss high school junior!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.15,0:08:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're amazing... Always in the top tier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.20,0:08:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki-san, do you have any weaknesses?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.00,0:08:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's rather embarrassing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.62,0:09:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But there are times when I just space out or get lost in my thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.40,0:09:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I've cut myself while using a slicer,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,rushed too much and tripped on myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.12,0:09:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,had my bag caught in a closing door...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.02,0:09:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Uwa!!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.73,0:09:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.49,0:09:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki-san, those aren't weaknesses... That's what we call moé.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.23,0:09:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, moé...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.50,0:09:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The klutzy girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.62,0:09:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of image was going through Kona-chan's head?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.22,0:09:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki-san, you're really good-looking, so why are you wearing glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.25,0:09:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You can only go for a certain type of guy with that look.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.57,0:09:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,"Go for..."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.11,0:09:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Putting attractiveness aside, haven't you thought about changing to contacts?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.12,0:09:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard that glasses can actually make your eyes worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.91,0:09:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, it's really embarrassing since I'm already in high school, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.16,0:09:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared of... contact lenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.45,0:09:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Or rather, putting things in my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.09,0:09:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't open my eyes underwater, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.78,0:09:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... This girl's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.26,0:09:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a real natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.84,0:09:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, isn't that Miyuki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.06,0:10:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if she's here for an eye exam to get contacts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.82,0:10:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she's just better off that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.05,0:10:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That looked like it hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.16,0:10:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a real natural...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Kagami's absent today because of a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.31,0:10:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but it doesn't seem like she has influenza.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.08,0:10:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm stupid, so I don't have to worry about catching something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.65,0:10:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard of colds, but being stupid works against influenza, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.90,0:10:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? A cold and influenza are different?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.96,0:10:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I just thought it was an upgraded version of a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.24,0:10:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.81,0:10:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But now that you mention it, I'm not sure anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.12,0:10:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? The difference between influenza and a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.12,0:10:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.37,0:10:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.83,0:10:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Influenza is transmitted via a virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.60,0:10:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,High fevers, sore muscles and fatigue are common symptoms,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.96,0:10:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's the chance that you can have multiple symptoms at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.81,0:11:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, symptoms of the common cold usually include a swollen throat or runny nose, and fevers aren't as high.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There are also some other minute differences.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.41,0:11:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, they are two different illnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.92,0:11:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.43,0:11:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...there are some overlapping symptoms, so I guess you could call it the upgraded version of a cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.07,0:11:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Kona-chan, why the long face?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.24,0:11:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's nothing big, but I was just thinking about the conversation we had this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.18,0:11:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? The one about the cold and influenza?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.33,0:11:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa, you didn't deny it when I said I was stupid...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.25,0:11:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No! That's not what I meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.47,0:11:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Konata-chan, welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.91,0:11:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She came to visit Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.75,0:11:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, thank you for coming all the way over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.73,0:11:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the intrusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.61,0:11:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagami... You've got a pretty cute face when you sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.90,0:12:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here!? Go home!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.01,0:12:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey... You woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.32,0:12:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Visit?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.14,0:12:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.99,0:12:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You came all the way over here to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.69,0:12:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.65,0:12:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't want to give it to you or anything, so I'll just accept the thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.33,0:12:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, how nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There's the new virus that's circulating, so she was probably worried about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.60,0:12:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that she only cared about games and anime, but... I'm a little touched.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.99,0:12:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I also wanted to see the homework that was assigned the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.48,0:12:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And I got to see a pretty good sleeping face, so don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.68,0:12:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.96,0:12:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagami, Miyuki-chan came to visit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.18,0:12:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.41,0:12:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to intrude.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to make you come over on your holiday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.02,0:12:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay for you to be up like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.40,0:12:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.67,0:12:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.78,0:12:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a lot better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.45,0:12:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,My fever's gone down after I took some medicine, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.25,0:12:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.79,0:12:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wa... I'm so happy to get flowers and fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.54,0:12:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.87,0:12:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.64,0:13:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to come visit you with Izumi-san and the others, but I was busy that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.08,0:13:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.83,0:13:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I have some documents from the Student Council meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.81,0:13:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.00,0:13:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If you could just take a look at them, I'd appreciate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.96,0:13:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.79,0:13:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, here are the budget sheets for some clubs, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.79,0:13:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm making your cold worse, I'll just go home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.90,0:13:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what a visit should be like...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.53,0:13:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.28,0:13:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing is, Konata came by yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.29,0:13:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.16,0:13:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe that's Izumi-san's way of showing that she cares.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.55,0:13:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,About the homework thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.87,0:13:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe she was just doing it to humour you and make you feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.18,0:13:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And the sleeping face ordeal may have been inevitable... Her way of being considerate and not causing a ruckus.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.76,0:13:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Can this woman only think positively!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.04,0:13:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't even come up with scenarios like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.05,0:13:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, Tsukasa-san isn't here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.07,0:14:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Mornin'...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.39,0:14:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, do you feel any better?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.02,0:14:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see, she's a lot more laid back than a sick person.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.61,0:14:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.01,0:14:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not usually like this, but I was up until dawn...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.06,0:14:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.62,0:14:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.99,0:14:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Lately, I've been having trouble waking up myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.96,0:14:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, don't you feel sleepy lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.88,0:14:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Since today is especially warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.47,0:14:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, yep... So true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing we can do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.63,0:14:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how our other holiday was really warm, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.26,0:14:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.08,0:14:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,When I woke up, the sun was already setting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.92,0:14:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I slept that whole day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.16,0:14:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You should rest while you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.96,0:14:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I was in my pajamas all day that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.04,0:14:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'm in my pajamas right now, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.66,0:14:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Those things you're wearing right now; those are you pajamas?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.57,0:14:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.76,0:14:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They're so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.44,0:15:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't look like pajamas at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.13,0:15:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.02,0:15:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Truly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.77,0:15:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I can just stay looking like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.73,0:15:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.29,0:15:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You could even walk outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.96,0:15:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I can go to the convenience store.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.12,0:15:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There seems to be no end to this stupid conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.52,0:15:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I gained weight...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.28,0:15:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.07,0:15:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's bra has wires and a little extra padding, so that must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.71,0:15:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... I wonder how many grams it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.71,0:15:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If I subtract it, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.03,0:15:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.61,0:15:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.97,0:15:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I totally forgot today was the physical exam,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.08,0:15:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,so I wore my character printed underwear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.72,0:15:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How embarrassing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.83,0:15:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't grown at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.62,0:15:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you... you're the only one that looks secure!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.31,0:15:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.46,0:15:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.15,0:15:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.59,0:15:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.08,0:15:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.73,0:15:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagami, you come here often... Don't you have any friends in your own class?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.21,0:15:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't compare me to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.85,0:15:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to pick a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.85,0:16:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And here, I thought you were an outcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.63,0:16:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you be worrying about yourself since you have no social skills?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.37,0:16:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.41,0:16:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I may look like this, but I've got almost a hundred friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.24,0:16:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and my social and bartering skills are pretty high.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.68,0:16:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I even join parties every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.53,0:16:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.07,0:16:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,With my party members, I restored the glimmering crystals so the world wouldn't end,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.04,0:16:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And one time we saved the kidnapped princ{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.08,0:16:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're talking about a game, aren't you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.94,0:16:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But I haven't seen that person lately...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.29,0:16:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.97,0:16:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably a friend she has in the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, he's a warrior-class character.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.50,0:16:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he was going to go level up his combat skill,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.43,0:16:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,so he went to an area with lots of monsters, but I haven't seen him since.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.98,0:16:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.27,0:16:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Another person told me he's camping out in an underground cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.63,0:16:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's wondering if he's okay... He's locked himself up in there and hasn't come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.19,0:16:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He's isolating himself in a game?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.90,0:16:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not too sure about the details, but based on the login info, it seems like he's been logged on the entire time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.84,0:16:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So he has no life, physically and virtually!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.86,0:17:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's the same person controlling his character.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, Tsukasa and Konata, how did you two become friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.76,0:17:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa was about to get kidnapped by a huge foreigner,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.38,0:17:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but right at that moment, I appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.96,0:17:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I saved her using my jabs and gracefully executed a whirlwind kick,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.38,0:17:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,saving her from certain danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.73,0:17:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you always start talking about games halfway through a conversation?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.18,0:17:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, in reality, I just exchanged fists with an experienced fighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.22,0:17:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not so sure about resorting to violence right away, but you've got some good points.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.88,0:17:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is, a foreigner was trying to ask me for directions, but I had no clue what he was saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.34,0:17:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's when Konata appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.41,0:17:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha{\fscx300}-{\r}!? And you tried to pick a fight with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.02,0:17:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This season has come again...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.68,0:17:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.04,0:17:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, I was just thinking about how it's baseball season again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.12,0:17:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't watch sports?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.60,0:17:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so athletic, so I could imagine you watching things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.21,0:17:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, when they go into overtime...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.20,0:17:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The later programs get bumped down and my recording times get all screwed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.26,0:18:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,In the worst cases, the show disappears altogether.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.08,0:18:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't feel good when something you like disappears, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.19,0:18:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagami, when do you eat the strawberry on a strawberry short-cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.12,0:18:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.12,0:18:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if you were the type that saved the best for last.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.31,0:18:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true. I do tend to save my favorites until the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.10,0:18:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,but eating the strawberry really depends on how I feel at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.33,0:18:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Then do you cook negi-tan shio on both sides?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.85,0:18:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Salted beef tongue with onions?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.11,0:18:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it cooks pretty fast as it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.29,0:18:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,but I guess it'll cook even faster if I flip it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.87,0:18:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.82,0:18:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The onions will fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.26,0:18:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You don't put the onions on top after they're done cooking?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.93,0:18:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do that, then the onions will be raw.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.12,0:18:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the onions are just for flavor, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.35,0:18:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You just don't get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe you can do it either way?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.14,0:18:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.05,0:18:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think the head of a Choco Cornet is the fat side or the skinny side?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.33,0:18:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The fat side?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.26,0:18:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's what I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.79,0:18:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha... Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.16,0:18:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Then which side do you eat it from?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.52,0:18:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I tear the skinny side and use it to scoop the extra chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.90,0:18:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.21,0:18:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.84,0:19:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever made any real friends other than us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.88,0:19:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I had a really close friend when I was in middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.80,0:19:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa... You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.13,0:19:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't talked to her in a while, but I wonder what she's doing right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.20,0:19:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,In middle school, she wrote that her dream was to become a mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.71,0:19:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So she was just like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.94,0:19:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky Channel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.68,0:19:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oha-lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.90,0:19:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's begun! Lucky Channel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.12,0:19:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We're finally on TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.90,0:19:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,For those of you who are watching for the first time, hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.95,0:19:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the navigator, Kogami Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm Shiraishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.17,0:19:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Who...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.87,0:19:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.27,0:19:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,From here on, this person is going to be my helper.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.07,0:19:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiraishi Minoru-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.67,0:19:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Panpaka pa~n!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.88,0:20:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Uh... I'm going to be Akira-sama's assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.66,0:20:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Shiraishi Minoru. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.72,0:20:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiraishi-san, you're so tense.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.76,0:20:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our chance to be on TV, so loosen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.68,0:20:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry... I'm not used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.53,0:20:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's get down to business.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.13,0:20:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got some postcards from our viewers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.90,0:20:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.76,0:20:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This one's from Beriko-Lover-san from Osaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.92,0:20:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,"Congratulations on the TV show debut of Lucky Channel!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.80,0:20:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you~!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.66,0:20:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,"I have a question for Akira-san."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.33,0:20:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,"I understand you're an uber-idol, Akira-san, but how much do idols make?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.62,0:20:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,"Please tell me."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.38,0:20:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Salary?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.10,0:20:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.38,0:20:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This seems like a very direct question.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.71,0:20:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.20,0:20:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you gonna do after you find out?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.88,0:20:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Akira-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.63,0:20:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If you really wanna know, I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.07,0:20:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,To be quite honest, it could be anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.53,0:20:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There are times where the pay itself is pretty cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.34,0:20:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But I guess it's like a kickback from the management office.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.54,0:20:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,My position's fixed, so I'm not exactly sure on the percentage they're keeping from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.82,0:21:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that, I've been doing this since I was 3 years old,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.58,0:21:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,so all of my pay is deposited into my parents' account.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.32,0:21:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,All I get out of it is a puny allowance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.98,0:21:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And I mean puny.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.57,0:21:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it... My mom's been sportin' some brand-name goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.92,0:21:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That isn't coming from my pay, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.08,0:21:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotta be kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.76,0:21:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not Cinderella!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.76,0:21:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Just cuz dad's been holding back on his cash recently,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.65,0:21:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Uh, I don't think you have to tell them that much...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.28,0:21:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...doesn't mean you can start taking my money!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.42,0:21:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.71,0:21:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to say goodbye already.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.46,0:21:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira's so lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.64,0:21:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this corner is for you guys to ask me questions or send me requests,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.74,0:21:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,or let me know what you think of the show. Please~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.70,0:21:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiraishi-san, you say "please" for them, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.85,0:21:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh, well, then... Please watch us again next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.21,0:21:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,See you again!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.71,0:21:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, is it true you're gonna be in the actual series?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.25,0:21:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, where did you hear that from?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.60,0:21:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while since the four of us have gone out to karaoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.26,0:21:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I rarely come to places like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.46,0:22:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon. We only got two hours, so let's sing, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.91,0:22:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. We've got plenty of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.86,0:22:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.32,0:22:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.03,0:22:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels good when you sing your heart out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.85,0:22:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where's the catalog?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.16,0:22:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Catalog?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.96,0:22:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the catalog.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.16,0:22:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The catalog?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.36,0:22:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the thing with all the songs and their numbers 'n stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.62,0:22:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.84,0:22:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.37,0:22:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then. I'll start it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.91,0:22:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa. You already put three songs in?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.15,0:22:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's such a waste if you don't sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.90,0:22:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, ah, ah... Test, test, test.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.18,0:22:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this song?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.90,0:22:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,"Uchuu Tetsujin Kyoudain!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.46,0:22:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You always have to start off with this song!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.79,0:22:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an1}Never heard of it.
